brisk (1.0~beta1.2) stable; urgency=low

  * Switch to debian-native package numbering, since we ship packaging stuff
    in orig.tar.gz
  * Relax java dependency to allow openjdk use with lib packages, if people
    really really want to do so. We strongly recommend sticking with the sun
    jvm.
  * Still recommend at least version 6.24-1~squeeze1 of the sun jvm
  * add dependencies for awk, procps, and lsb-base to brisk
  * add Conflicts: with cassandra as well as apache-cassandra.
  * Build-Depends on thrift-compiler, ant-optional

 -- paul cannon <paul@datastax.com>  Mon, 09 May 2011 16:24:14 -0500

